{"title_page": "List of newspapers in Greece", "text_new": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\nThe number of national daily [[newspapers]] in [[Greece]] was 68 in 1950, and it increased to 156 in 1965.<ref>{{cite book|title=A Virtuous Circle: Political Communications in Post-Industrial Societies|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=New York|url=http://www.hks.harvard.edu/fs/pnorris/Acrobat/VIRTUOUS/CHAPTER4.PDF|author=Pippa Norris|accessdate=6 October 2013|chapter=Chapter 4 The Decline of Newspapers?|date=Fall 2000}}</ref> Below is a list of newspapers published in Greece.\n\n==Greek daily newspapers==\n\n:{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n! Title\n! Established\n! Owner\n! Sunday Edition\n! Political orientation\n\n|-\n| ''Dimokratia'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Dimokratikos Typos buys into Estia Newspaper|url=https://www.advertising.gr/media/i-dimokratikos-typos-symmetechei-stin-estia-60702/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || 2010 || Dimokratikos Typos SA || Yes || [[Centre-right]]\n|-\n| ''Efimerida ton Syntakton'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Efimerida ton Syntakton|url=https://el.wikipedia.org/wiki/%CE%97_%CE%95%CF%86%CE%B7%CE%BC%CE%B5%CF%81%CE%AF%CE%B4%CE%B1_%CF%84%CF%89%CE%BD_%CE%A3%CF%85%CE%BD%CF%84%CE%B1%CE%BA%CF%84%CF%8E%CE%BD|publisher=Wikipedia}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || 2012 || Anexartita Mesa Maziki Enimerosis SA || Yes  || [[Left-wing politics|Left]] [[Centre Left]]\n|-\n| ''Eleftheri Ora'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Eleftheri Ora|url=http://www.argosmis.gr/index.php?page=16&cat=0,1&ID=85741&Code_id=22781|publisher=Argos Distribution}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || 1981 || \u039cV Press Ltd || Yes || [[Right-wing]]\n|-\n| ''[[Eleftheros Typos]]'' || 1916 || SABD Ekdotiki SA || Yes || [[Liberal conservative]]\n|-\n| ''[[Estia]]'' || 1876 || Estia Newspaper SA || Yes || [[Conservative]]\n|-\n| ''[[I Avgi]]'' || 1952 || I Avgi Ekdotikos & Dimosiografikos Organismos SA || Yes ||[[Left-wing]]\n|-\n| ''[[Kathimerini]]'' || 1919 || Kathimerini Publishing SA || Yes || [[Liberal conservative]]\n|-\n| ''Kontra News'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Kontra Media Group|url=https://el.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kouris_Media_Group|publisher=Wikipedia}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || 2013 || Kouris Media Group || Yes || [[Left-wing]]\n|-\n| ''O Logos'' <ref>{{cite web|title=O Logos Newspaper|url=http://www.argosmis.gr/index.php?page=16&cat=0,1&ID=52568&Code_id=25135|publisher=Argos Distribution}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || 1990 || Neo Typografiki MIKE || Yes || [[Centre Left]]\n|-\n| ''[[Rizospastis]]'' || 1916 || [[Communist Party of Greece]] || Yes || [[Communist]]\n|-\n| ''[[Ta Nea]]'' || 1931 || [[Evangelos Marinakis|Alter Ego Media SA]] || Yes || [[Centre Left]]\n|-\n\n|}\n\n===Greek daily specialized content newspapers===\n\n:{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n! Title\n! Established\n! Owner\n! Sunday Edition\n! Type\n\n|-\n| ''[[Naftemporiki]]'' || 1924 || P Athanasiadis & Partners SA || Yes || [[Financial]]\n|-\n| ''Espresso News'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Espresso News retains title for Giannis Filippakis|url=https://www.ereportaz.gr/kleinei-i-espresso-toy-filippaki-anoigei-i-espresso-toy-syrmogloy/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || 1983 || Estia Ependitiki SA || Yes || [[Tabloid journalism|Tabloid]]\n|-\n| ''Makeleio'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Stefanos Chios|url=https://el.wikipedia.org/wiki/%CE%A3%CF%84%CE%AD%CF%86%CE%B1%CE%BD%CE%BF%CF%82_%CE%A7%CE%AF%CE%BF%CF%82|publisher=Wikipedia}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || 2015 || Makeleio Ltd || Yes || [[Tabloid journalism|Tabloid]]\n|-\n| ''Star Press'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Ellinikos Typos|url=http://www.argosmis.gr/index.php?page=16&cat=0,1&ID=61856&Code_id=38991|publisher=Argos Distribution}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || N/A || Ellinikos Typos SA || Yes || [[Tabloid journalism|Tabloid]]\n|-\n\n|}\n\n===Greek daily sports newspapers===\n\n:{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n! Title\n! Affiliation\n\n|-\n| ''Fos'' || [[Olympiacos]]\n|-\n| ''Gavros'' || Olympiacos\n|-\n| ''Kokkinos Protathlitis'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u039a\u03cc\u03ba\u03ba\u03b9\u