ia}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || 2008 || Free Sunday Ekdotiki SA || [[Alternative weekly]]\n|-\n| ''Thessaloniki'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Thessaloniki Free Press|url=https://www.makthes.gr/free-press}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || 2019 || Makedonia Enimerosi SA || [[Alternative weekly]]\n|-\n\n|}\n\n===Greek weekly specialized content newspapers===\n\n:{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n! Title\n! Type\n\n|-\n| ''Apopsi'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Apopsi Archive|url=https://www.iapopsi.gr/entypi-ekdosi-2020//}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || [[Financial]]\n|-\n| ''Axia News'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Axia News|url=https://el.wikipedia.org/wiki/%CE%97_%CE%91%CE%BE%CE%AF%CE%B1_(%CE%B5%CF%86%CE%B7%CE%BC%CE%B5%CF%81%CE%AF%CE%B4%CE%B1)|publisher=Wikipedia}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || [[Financial]]\n|-\n| ''Deal News'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Deal News cover pages|url=https://www.naftemporiki.gr/frontpages/latest/ebdomadiaies/deal-news/full|publisher=Naftemporiki}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>  || [[Financial]]\n|-\n| ''[[Eleftheros Kosmos]]'' || [[Nationalist]]\n|-\n| ''Orthodoxi Alithia'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u039f\u03c1\u03b8\u03cc\u03b4\u03bf\u03be\u03b7 \u0391\u03bb\u03ae\u03b8\u03b5\u03b9\u03b1|url=https://el.wikipedia.org/wiki/%CE%95%CF%86%CE%B7%CE%BC%CE%B5%CF%81%CE%AF%CE%B4%CE%B1_%22%CE%9F%CF%81%CE%B8%CF%8C%CE%B4%CE%BF%CE%BE%CE%B7_%CE%91%CE%BB%CE%AE%CE%B8%CE%B5%CE%B9%CE%B1%22|publisher=Wikipedia}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || [[Greek_Orthodox_Church|Religion]]\n|-\n| ''Orthodoxos Typos'' <ref>{{cite web|title=Orthodoxos Typos|url=https://orthodoxostypos.gr/efimeris-orthodoxos-tipos/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || [[Greek_Orthodox_Church|Religion]]\n|-\n| ''Stilos Orthodoxias'' (bi-monthly) <ref>{{cite web|title=Stilos Orthodoxias |url=https://orthodoxia.gr/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref> || [[Greek_Orthodox_Church|Religion]]\n|-\n| ''[[Stochos]]'' || [[National conservatism|National Conservatism]]\n|-\n\n|}\n\n===Greek weekly betting newspapers===\n\n:{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Title\n\n|-\n| ''12X''\n|-\n| ''Kingbet''\n|-\n| 