ine.gr/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n*''Tharos'' <ref>{{cite web|title= \u0398\u03ac\u03c1\u03c1\u03bf\u03c2 (\u039c\u03b5\u03c3\u03c3\u03b7\u03bd\u03af\u03b1)|url=http://www.tharrosnews.gr/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Pieria_(regional_unit)|Pieria]]'''\n*''Olympio Vima'' <ref>{{cite web|title= \u039f\u03bb\u03cd\u03bc\u03c0\u03b9\u03bf \u0392\u03ae\u03bc\u03b1|url=http://olympiobima.gr/protoselida}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n*''Politia Epta'' <ref>{{cite web|title= \u03a0\u03bf\u03bb\u03b97\u03b5\u03af\u03b1|url=https://issuu.com/eptanews|publisher=Isuu}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Preveza]]'''\n*''Topiki Foni'' <ref>{{cite web|title= \u03a4\u03bf\u03c0\u03b9\u03ba\u03ae \u03a6\u03c9\u03bd\u03ae|url=https://www.topikifoni.gr/protoselido.php}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Rhodope_(regional_unit)|Rodopi]]'''\n*''Chronos'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u03a7\u03c1\u03cc\u03bd\u03bf\u03c2|url=https://www.xronos.gr/profile}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n*''Paratititis Thrakis'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u03a0\u03b1\u03c1\u03b1\u03c4\u03b7\u03c1\u03b7\u03c4\u03ae\u03c2 \u0398\u03c1\u03ac\u03ba\u03b7\u03c2|url=https://www.paratiritis-news.gr/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n*''Thrakiki Agora'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u0398\u03c1\u03b1\u03ba\u03b9\u03ba\u03ae \u0391\u03b3\u03bf\u03c1\u03ac|url=https://www.thrakikiagora.gr/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Serres]]'''\n*''Simerini'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u03a3\u03b7\u03bc\u03b5\u03c1\u03b9\u03bd\u03ae|url=https://www.e-simerini.com/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n*''Kathimerinos Paratiritis'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u039a\u03b1\u03b8\u03b7\u03bc\u03b5\u03c1\u03b9\u03bd\u03cc\u03c2 \u03a0\u03b1\u03c1\u03b1\u03c4\u03b7\u03c1\u03b7\u03c4\u03ae\u03c2|url=http://www.serresparatiritis.gr/index.php?category_id=41&page=first_page}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Thessaloniki]]'''\n*''Typos Thessalonikis'' <ref>{{cite web|title= \u03a4\u03cd\u03c0\u03bf\u03c2 \u0398\u03b5\u03c3\u03c3\u03b1\u03bb\u03bf\u03bd\u03af\u03ba\u03b7\u03c2 |url=https://www.typosthes.gr/issues}}{{in lang|el}}