a]]'''\n*''Proinos Tipos'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u03a0\u03c1\u03c9\u03b9\u03bd\u03cc\u03c2 \u03a4\u03cd\u03c0\u03bf\u03c2|url=http://www.proinos-typos.gr/i-taftotita-tou-p-t/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Elis_(regional_unit)|Elia]]'''\n*''Patris'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u03a0\u03b1\u03c4\u03c1\u03af\u03c2 (\u0397\u03bb\u03b5\u03af\u03b1)|url=https://www.patrisnews.com/diafora/protoselida/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n*''Proti'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u03a0\u03c1\u03ce\u03c4\u03b7|url=https://www.protinews.gr/issues-archive}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Euboea|Evia]]'''\n*''Evoiki Gnomi'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u0395\u03c5\u03b2\u03bf\u03ca\u03ba\u03ae \u0393\u03bd\u03ce\u03bc\u03b7|url=https://www.egnomi.gr/egnomi.php}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Evritania]]'''\n*''Evritanika Nea'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u0395\u03c5\u03c4\u03b7\u03c4\u03b1\u03bd\u03b9\u03ba\u03ac \u039d\u03ad\u03b1|url=https://www.evrytanika.gr/index.php?option=com_content&view=category&layout=blog&id=120&Itemid=250}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Fokida]]'''\n*''Empros Nafpaktou''  <ref>{{cite web|title=\u0395\u03bc\u03c0\u03c1\u03cc\u03c2 \u039d\u03b1\u03c5\u03c0\u03ac\u03ba\u03c4\u03bf\u03c5|url=https://www.emprosnews.gr/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n*''Ora tis Fokidas''  <ref>{{cite web|title=\u03a9\u03c1\u03b1 \u03c4\u03b7\u03c2 \u03a6\u03c9\u03ba\u03af\u03b4\u03b1\u03c2|url=http://www.orafok.gr/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Fthiotida]]'''\n*''Lamiakos Typos'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u039b\u03b1\u03bc\u03b9\u03b1\u03ba\u03cc\u03c2 \u03a4\u03cd\u03c0\u03bf\u03c2|url=http://www.lamiakos-typos.gr/news}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Heraklion]] Crete'''\n*''Nea Kriti'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u039d\u03ad\u03b1 \u039a\u03c1\u03ae\u03c4\u03b7|url=https://www.neakriti.gr/protoselida/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n*''Patris'' <ref>{{cite web|title=\u03a0\u03b1\u03c4\u03c1\u03af\u03c2 (\u039a\u03c1\u03ae\u03c4\u03b7)|url=https://www.patris.gr/}}{{in lang|el}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Ioannina]]'''\n*''Anexartitos Typos'' <ref>{{cite 