CEF6\"\n| align=\"center\" | 2011\n| align=\"left\" | [[Indonesia International]]\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|INA}} [[Fransisca Ratnasari]]\n| align=\"left\" | 21\u201316, 21\u201311\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:white\" | {{gold1}} '''Winner'''\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#D8CEF6\"\n| align=\"center\" | 2011\n| align=\"left\" | [[Maldives International]]\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|IND}} [[P. C. Thulasi|P.&nbsp;C. Thulasi]]\n| align=\"left\" | 21\u201311, 21\u201316\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:white\" | {{gold1}} '''Winner'''\n|-\n|- style=\"background:#D8CEF6\"\n| align=\"center\" | 2010\n| align=\"left\" | [[Iran Fajr International]]\n| align=\"left\" | {{flagicon|JPN}} [[Rie Eto (badminton)|Rie Eto]]\n| align=\"left\" | 14\u201321, 24\u201326\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:white\" | {{silver2}} '''Runner-up'''\n|}\n:{{Color box|#D8CEF6|border=darkgray}} [[BWF International Challenge]] tournament\n:{{Color box|#D5D5D5|border=darkgray}} [[BWF International Series]] tournament\n\n==Career overview==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Singles\n! Played\n! Wins\n! Losses\n! Balance\n|-\n| align=left | '''Total'''\n| 468\n| 328\n| 140\n| '''+188'''\n|-\n| align=left | '''Current year''' (2020)\n| 8\n| 5\n| 3\n| '''+2'''\n|}\n\n{{col-2}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! Doubles\n! Played\n! Wins\n! Losses\n! Balance\n|-\n| align=left | '''Total'''\n| 20\n| 10\n| 10\n| '''0'''\n|-\n| align=left | '''Current year''' (2020)\n| 0\n| 0\n| 0\n| '''0'''\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n:''<nowiki>*</nowiki> Statistics were last updated on 17 March 2020.''<ref>{{cite web|title=PUSARLA V. Sindhu \u2013 Career overview|url=http://bwfbadminton.com/player/73173/pusarla-v-sindhu|website=bwfbadminton.com|publisher=[[Badminton World Federation]]|accessdate=20 December 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Singles performance timeline===\n{|class=wikitable style=text-align:center\n|-\n!width=260|Tournament!!200